desc: Founded on the basis of Nature to Nurture, Dab Herb Makeup and Skin Care holds itself to a holistic approach to skin care & makeup. Using the best of food-grade, cruelty-free, certified organic, and vegan ingredients available to us, each of our products are handmade with quality and purity in mind.

layout.text: Welcome to the healthiest decision you've made yet.

dabherbmakeup.com is home to Dab Herb Makeup's Sustainable Luxury line— a new sister line harnessing the power of even more luxuriant ingredients and even further employing conscientious and sustainable practices
